# Component Creator Settings

## Default Component Type

Preferred location for new components:

```yaml
defaultComponentType: ui  # Options: ui, custom
```

## Figma Integration

Figma API token (optional - for automated design extraction):

```yaml
figmaApiToken: ""  # Leave empty to be prompted each time
```

## Auto-Test Generation

Automatically generate comprehensive test files:

```yaml
autoGenerateTests: true  # Options: true, false
```

## Design System Validation

Enforce CSS variable usage (recommended):

```yaml
validateCssVariables: true  # Options: true, false
strictValidation: true      # Block commits with hardcoded colors
```

## Storybook Documentation

Auto-generate comprehensive Storybook stories:

```yaml
autoGenerateStories: true        # Options: true, false
includeDesignTokensTable: true   # Include CSS variables table
includeTypographyTable: true     # Include font specifications
includeUsageExamples: true       # Include code examples
```

## Component Analysis

Behavior for component existence checks:

```yaml
checkExistingComponents: true    # Always check before creating
suggestVariants: true            # Suggest variants over new components
identifySubcomponents: true      # Find reusable components
```

## Responsive Design

Enforce responsive design patterns:

```yaml
requireResponsiveDesign: true    # Ensure mobile-first approach
enforceBreakpoints: true         # Require breakpoint usage
```

## Registry Updates

Automatically update component registry:

```yaml
autoUpdateRegistry: true         # Update components.yaml
autoUpdateExports: true          # Update src/index.ts
runIntegrityCheck: true          # Run integrity snapshot (UI components)
```

